{
  "stem": "5516.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the only thing is, the president from the ghetto decided older people and married people not to send them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Just single and young one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I and my brother they send out there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, and I worked there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I didn't work in-- like the other people, heavy work, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I worked-- they had a brush shop.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I made the brushes for the airport, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A couple of years.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after this, they put us, maybe, for eight months or the year, I  was in this camp, you know, in the barracks from the airport.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Siauliai.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they had a name for the airport, like we got here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember the name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A military.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Military.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This military, not civil.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They used to come in, we had pilots there from Italy, you know, all the allies from Germany.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They used to take off with the planes and bomb.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We used to load-- the people from the Jewish ghetto, they used to load the bombs, you know, in the planes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I used to do.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Me and my brother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The youngest one.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, Israel.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The barracks was-- you see, the commandant, he was nice to us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after this, when the SS took over the ghetto, we had old people and kids-- 900.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So one day, he come over with police, I think-- Lithuanian police, or Ukrainian police, or military.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they put them on buses, you know, the kids.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That they took out my sister's two kids, and I think my brother's kids, and 800 more.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They took they out and they destroyed them, must be.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, this is--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When they took out the kids, they come over with nurses, you know, nice German nurses.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
